### OAuth 模块 — 客户端凭证 / 客户端注册

### @name clientCredentials
# @no-log
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grant_type": "client_credentials",
  "client_id": "my-client",
  "client_secret": "your-client-secret"
}

> {%
  if (response.body.data && response.body.data.access_token) {
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.access_token);
  }
%}

###

### @name createOAuthClient
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client_id": "my-client",
  "client_secret": "your-client-secret",
  "client_name": "第三方应用",
  "scope": "read"
}

###

### @name listOAuthClients
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/clients?page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name getOAuthClient
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/clients/my-client
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
